                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/62957645/">Minerva</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2014-03-16</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">挂康长素的羊头卖“贬共和、退西方，讨孙文”的狗药，立意不高，论证无力</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="527525809">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-527525809" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-527525809" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="527525809">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Genc/">Joseph.C</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar30 rating" title="还行"></span>
                    <span>2012-05-04</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">让我反感的三点：一是伪文言，虽然伪却也继承了文言重形式轻内容的啰嗦劲；二是无章法，无论证逻辑，行文上颇似政治宣传；三是夹带私货，假托康有为之口宣扬作者个人的“保守主义”政治思想。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="959265313">
